Write a flask server which has a scoreboard for a ctf. It should have a database which has a list of all of the ctf activities, a tables with all of the users and what activities each user has accomplished. Make a login for admins, and use 2fa. Make a page for admins to edit users and the activities that each user has done, as well as add activities. Each activity should be worth a certain amount of points, and there should be a scoreboard comparing every user. Use sqlite